  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This project will make it possible to better understand the natural history of Cohen Syndrom
      and the phenotypes associated with mutations in the VPS13B gene, to improve the therapeutic
      management of patients. It will also provide a better description of Cohen-like syndrome for
      genetic counselling for the families concerned.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
